= A generic type for classes that receive data buffers as results =

The BufferOperationListener type allows a class to declare that it is able to
receive a data buffer as a result of an operation.

= to_event_receiver =

Wrap this event listener object to a standard EventReceiver object. Any boolean or
Error values will then be treated appropriately, and passed to the original object.

= on_buffer =

Called when an operation has a data buffer to submit.
